Text.string: I have no mouth and I MUST HAVE A MOUTH!
I was born this way! WHAT'S YOUR EXCUSE?!
I wriggle on the line for NOBODY!
Coming innnn! HOT! [slightly deranged, with innuendo]
This is gonna get hairy... REAL hairy!
This is why I wear the pants around here!
Clear the line! We have guests to belittle!
The path to the Great Vault is paved in VISCERA!
Fragile things! They softly cry and weep!
Lick me... I'm sweet as acid AND twice as nasty.
“Like a second skin” is NOT a euphemism!
You picked the wrong way to scream!
WHAT'S THE FLIPPY THING ON A MAILBOX CALLED? I MUST KNOW!
DO I LOOK REALLY BIG RIGHT NOW?
Get dusty for me! Reeeeaaal dusty.
You are a figment of my digestion!
Don't worry, I'm gonna braid your hair... [sinister]
I am just DROWNING in credit card offers.
We pick and chew and gnash and gnaw!
And frankly, nobody cares about you.
Concentrate! Get the kill! You can do it!
Your lungs are in bone jail!
That's right! And now... for dinner... [creepy laughter]
Make like a tree and -- WHAT'S A TREE?!
You have deciduous ears! AND I AM AUTUMN!
I'm not a cannibal! YOU'RE AN ANIMAL!
We rake ourselves across the flames!
Stop staring at the entrails in my organ jail!
New faces, for the WHOLE FAMILY!
Pick apart the parasites, convert or destroy!
I yearn for a more civilized era!
Smack chop like we never stop till the flesh runs out!
Your pretty façade! It mocks me!
No one kills my little brother but me!
Both legs are in it to win it!
You're gonna be my new corpse puppet!
If only we had a tricycle, we'd be thrice quick!
... which brings me to this VERY MOMENT!
The plot thickens! Like a beautiful red sauce!
Drape yourself upon the altar of my hunger!
I AM GOING TO EAT YOU!
Brother! They... they play like we do!
It's like my childhood! OH GLORIOUS!
I gave up opera tickets for THIS?
These triumphs pity not the luckless few!
A kill-steak! Yeah, I could eat!
My chompers sweat in the waiting. YOU HEAR ME?!
What have we ever done to you?! BESIDES TRYING TO EAT YOU?!
The meek shall inhabit the dirt!
They just keep not stopping IT'S AMAZING! [rising gradually the whole line, no pause]
I am a panopticon that is ALWAYS BLINKING.
My mouth sweats in antici... gah, PATION!
[sing-song] I know something you don't know!
I lost my mind. DO YOU HAVE IT?!
I CAN SHOW YOU SUCH THINGS!
Will you wear me as well as I do? Let's find out!
I just want to tell you a secret!
Act Two is ALWAYS the slowest, you assholes!
I left my mind with my keys! DO I EVEN HAVE KEYS?!
Your haunches will slake me. WHERE ARE YOU HIDING THEM?!
POP goes the weasel. YOU'RE THE WEASEL!
I'm gonna gunk up your whole day!
It was him or me! I chose HIM!
Strike where the iron is not!
What a game! The kids love it!
Don't call it a bum rakk!
Cut a jig you little bitch!
YI YI YI YI! [like Xena Warrior Princess' warcry]
If you can't handle me at my worst! Chew a different sausage!
Playtime or playtime, you tell ME.
You'll be a memory inside me forever!
You're gonna shit so hard, it'll stain your soul!
There's a puppet waiting to happen!
Well smash my entire face off!
Your organs are trapped in bone jail! Let me help!
Woman seeking viscera! Strong personality! Crazy hot!
What?! You don't LIKE being licked? [mouth open, tongue-y gnashing]
How many hearses do we need?!
Friends don't serve friends for dinner. But I'll happily eat yours.
Ooh, look at ME! I'm in a STABLE RELATIONSHIP!
Yes! No! Give me treats and -- GAH! Tell me what to do!
Just a crack of light inside... asking me to peek!
Let's go to a trade show and BUY A DOLPHIN!
First we're gonna tighten... THEN we're gonna SQUEEZE!
See my face, see it! [lower] Now see it.
Left bent and bleeding, slowly swallowed by dirt.
Masks don't make you special! Specialness does!
Why do you have a head on your head?!
You bottom feeder! GET AWAY FROM MY BOTTOM!
Finely removed... with a rip and a lullaby.
I don't care what the leaking looks like... I just want a spill!
Ohhh, the mess that's gonna be left...
Do you like how I dance? I've got zirconium pants!
Red leather piss leather! RED LEATHER PISS LEATHER!
WHY IS YOUR HEAD SO BRIGHT?!
I can see your shimmery designs!
Let's play “Who's Smoother”: my knife or your face!
Hiding or not, I still know you hear me...
Loose lips... are the BEST lips!
Take it away, miss lady fray!
Someone hold her down till I get there!
Let's ruin that pretty little face just a little more.
Something begs inside... I can hear it cry free...
Glam it up, sugar tits! It's time for the big disappointment!
Let's make those tattoos a little more permanent! Wink!
Okay, Sparkles: let's nail those feet to the ground, shall we?
Let's see if you still glow when you're in pieces!
Are we in your dream? Or mine?
I'm too young to blow up!
That's it, you're out of book club.
Let me hang heavy on your conscience.
HE was supposed to... be the one...
This is turning out to be a real bummer.
Put that experience to good use...
For the Calypsos, I gladly shatter!
I would have preferred a thank you!
Prison break... from the bone jail...
Keep... my... brother... away from... Lieberman...
Shoot my ashes at a quinceañera.
All that's real is me, and now I die!
I dream, I dream, and the construct shatters!
So I said, I'll take a dozen!
Oh, yeah! Gimme a lick! C'mon! C'mere! Someone give me a lick!
Spank and flay! The cheeky spreaders...
And THAT'S how you bury the lede! I'm a goddamn champion!
I love it when the pipsqueak squawks!
Be kind, let me rewind you -- all the way back before you began!
Never there. They were never there!
The game is a foot! A SEVERED FOOT!
There's one of me and none of you!
Can't hurt me if I'm not real!
But I got all glammed up!
Fine! Leave! BREAD BOWL FOR ONE!
Don't leave me alone with me! You psychopath!
But my buzzer is a buzzbuzzbuzzbuzz!
If you can't ride the wheel, don't roll!
Time for play time with little brother! [malicious giggle]
The hate factory! The windows go dark!
So many tooshies! Heading for the bushies!
I GOT ALL DRESSED UP FOR NOTHING?!
You're a dish out of chowder!
We are all but sacks of meat!
Didn't you read the terms and conditions?!
Do you like me?! Check yes or no!
I tried auto-cannibalism, but I'M A MANUAL!
I said I don't care! TAKE THE HINT!
That's why you plow the fetid field!
You are a travesty of majesty!
I am a beautiful bird! SCRAW!
Take my regard and suck it!
I am the finder of findeds!
Nobody disappears on me! Except mom!
I saw what you did! I think!
It's never like you were there!
Caught like a sphincter in an ass!
Really? Haven't we seen this before?
And lo! The dancing slaughter finally blossomed! Birthing an orgy of hedonistic optometrists!
You should be in a café!
I have four questions: why why why WHY?!
MAKE ME ONE WITH EVERYTHING! NO ONIONS!
Into the belly of the beast!
This is going in my novel!
Now the face, now the face!
What did I do to deserve you?
You can't have my gooey center!
Why is the sky so angry?!
It is for you that I am shrieking!
RAKKS! HOW COULD YOU? WE HAD A DEAL!
Damn it! Don't we have nets?!
If only I was a cannon ball!
That's it! I'm pooping on a pidgeon tomorrow!
Metal can still weep. Watch me.
Nice house! Got room for TWO?!
BUT DOES IT RUN ON LOVE?!
BANG, BOOM. THAT'S WHAT YOU SOUND LIKE!
I feel so close to you!
Step out of your shell, little bitch!
I've got a name with your cannon on it!
Don't worry, I always find the soft parts.
Don't stop, won't stop, can't stop the chop chop!
O-M-G! That look! I LOVE IT!
Canned man not in the can can!
Why did you LET HIM OUT?!
Two pretties for the price of FUN!
Can I interest you in a spine share?
The opposition only BELIEVES it's real!
I know unrealistic projections when I see them!
It's a good thing we lead with our noses!
It's a ruse! Show it we don't care!
It's a dummy! Give it licks!
Hey wait! Why are we doing this?!
THIS IS A NO FLY ZONE, ASSHOLE!
I have no blood for you!
Hey! That's mine! Give it back!
YOU MOTH! I'M NOT A FLAME!
Oh god! It's leeching my value!
I don't like it! I don't like it!
I'm already an obvious target! I don't need your help!
Totally fine. THIS IS TOTALLY FINE!
Why don't we ever talk anymore?!
Why would you do such a thing?!
Don't you get all cheeky on us!
Oh, THAT'S why they're shaped like that!
That's a lot of spilled milk, you monster!
I will conquer by my teeth skin!
You made them a floppy toy!
WE REHEARSED THIS! [doing scales very poorly] La la la LA la la la.
Good thing I stole your shoes this morning!
I KNEW it was your last birthday!
I have the weirdest déjà vu right now!
I'm gonna need a crock, to hold all this shit.
You'll never take me alive! WHICH I ASSUME WASN'T YOUR PLAN ANYWAY!
BUT HE WAS THE HALL MONITOR!
The world's a fishbowl -- I'M DROWNING!
